                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1103717798" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1103717798" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1103717798">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/4287011/">浅浅</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-10-30</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">有注音很重要，因为有很多字需要查字典，注了音就可以偷懒了。另外注释可以科普很多典故，看起来很有意思~</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1114511775">
        <div class="comment">
